Marin Hinkle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marin_Hinkle 0 Marin Elizabeth Hinkle (born March 23, 1966) is an American actress. Among several television and movie roles, she is best known for playing Judith Harper-Melnick on the CBS sitcom Two and a Half Men as well as Judy Brooks on the ABC television drama Once and Again and Rose Weissman in The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel.
